STUDENT ACCOMMODATION SYSTEM 
Requirements:

Module 1
Landlord Profile System ✅
Landlord Info page (public)
Detailed Info (private) ✅
Landlord rating from tenant
Building Rating
Roommate Profile System
Landing Info (public)
Detailed Info (private)
Rating from other roommates
Constraint
Profile Update
Add any new information
Update landlord’s name
Update contact number
Update email address
Create Accommodation Post
Show button to create post
Clicking button leads to form 
Filling up prompts in the form 
Clicking confirm button automatically posts
Update Accomodation Details
Show update button
Clicking button leads to accommodation form
Any prompt of the form can be changed
Clicking confirm button automatically updates the post

Module 2
 Accommodations List
Shows button for accommodation list under the profile
Clicking button leads to list of accommodations depending on profile type
If it is landlord then accommodation list shows number of properties registered and rented out
If it is tenant then list provides number of rented accommodation taken so far by the user
Clicking on an accommodation leads to details about the accommodation
 Roommate Request System
send and receive roommate requests 
Messaging system
Search location
Filter
Show a dropdown box
Toggle the box to show detailed information
Choose specific features to filter by such as rent and location
Clicking feature shortlist according to features chosen
 Hotline
Show a call icon 
Highlight icon when hovered over
Clicking of icon leads to list of hotline numbers
Clicking on a number automatically calls the hotline

Module 3
 Report
Show a button to report
Clicking button leads to a form
Form shows multiple reasons for reporting
Multiple submission automatically leads to post being removed temporarily
 Feedback
Show a button for feedback
Clicking button leads to a form
Form provides multiple options as well as a blank textbox to write feedback
Feedback is automatically posted to feedback channel
 Chat system
Show chatbox
Chatbox will pop-up when clicked
List of pre-prompted questions will be displayed
System will automatically answer questions based on chosen prompt
 Payment plan
Show payment window when confirming a property chosen
Show multiple payment options
If online payment is chosen, lead to payment gateway
Payment gateway connects with SSLCOMMERZ
 Rating
Show a button for rating
Clicking button shows a 5-star icon
Clicking on the number of stars rates the property
Rating is automatically updated and mean of rating is shown under property

Module 4
 Password change
Button to change password is shown under profile
Clicking button leads to providing the password for the profile as verification
If password matches, new window where password can be changes is opened
A new password has to be provided twice to confirm and change the password
 Language(if we can)
Show a language button
Toggling button shows drop down box
Clicking on language in the drop down box automatically translates page
Page is shown in the language chosen only
 Surveyed rating
Posting a property automatically leads to rating forms
Multiple rating form provide prompts to answer for multiple fields such as transport facilities near location and quality of property
Answers can be provided within a range of 5
Answering all prompts automatically provides a rating for the property from the system
 Password reset functionality using email
Show forgot password button
Clicking button leads to a text box prompting for email
When email is provided, it is matched with the email addresses in the database
If a match is found, an email is sent with automatically generated link for password change
Clicking on link leads to password change feature (requirement 16)
 Notification system
Show bell icon on top
Number of requests made or questions asked is shown on the bell
Clicking the icon leads to drop down box of the list of notifications
Clicking on a notification leads to the page
